# Real-time Rules

## Setup
- Socket.io server: `lib/socket-server.ts`
- Socket.io client: `lib/socket-client.ts`
- Authenticate every socket connection with session token
- Join rooms scoped to: `project:{id}`, `user:{id}`, `department:{id}`

## Events Naming Convention
- Client → Server: `client:action`  (e.g. `client:send-message`)
- Server → Client: `server:event`   (e.g. `server:new-message`)
- Errors:          `server:error`

## Security
- Validate all event payloads with Zod on the server
- Check room membership before broadcasting
- Rate limit events per socket connection
- Never broadcast sensitive data — fetch from API on client after notification